overview: Dee Williams is driving in her car and talking to her husband on the phone about their adult sons who are still living at home even though they are both around the age of 30. Dee arrives home and, as usual, the guys are playing video games and don't get up to help her bring in the groceries. Dee ends up dropping to the floor and dropping the groceries as they continue to play. Dante also mentions that he has an older girl that he has been messing around with that is around Dee's age and Dee listens intently, as if a plan to get them out of the house is forming in real time.
title: A Push From the Nest
